==Storage Options==
:''See also: [[Keg#Storage Options|Keg storage options]], [[Crafting#Crafted goods outside the farm|Crafted goods outside the farm]]''
While Preserves Jars can be stored anywhere on the farm, it is more space efficient to store them [[Keg#Inside Farm Buildings|inside farm buildings]] or [[Keg#Outside The Farm|outside the farm]] altogether.

==Trivia==
*The description of the Preserves Jar states that it makes Jam, but it actually produces Jelly.
*The description of the Preserves Jar was not updated to include fish roe or caviar in [[Version History#1.4|v1.4]].

